public final class BytesToBytesMap.MapIteratorWithKeyIndex extends Object implements Iterator<BytesToBytesMap.Location>
Iterator for the entries of this map. This is to first iterate over key indices in `longArray` then accessing values in `dataPages`. NOTE: this is different from `MapIterator` in the sense that key index is preserved here (See `UnsafeHashedRelation` for example of usage).
